				<p><a href="../">SMS-CV</a></p>
				<p><em>2009</em></p>
				<p><em class="background">&ndash; Empowering careers for the net-deprived.</em></p>
				<br />
				<p>The cell phone penetration in India is 87% as compared to the 8% of internet penetration. Users send a SMS with the email ID of their prospective employer to SMS-CV, and SMS-CV sends their CVs in an email to the employer. Thus enabling millions from the lower economic strataâ€™s who live in urban areas and lack an internet connection.</p>

<p><br /></p>

<p><b>role:</b> Conceptualization, Software Development.</p>

